cat <<EOF > .gitmessage
# <type>(<scope>): <subject> BREW-XXX
# Example: fix(eks): BREW-82 add force_delete to ECR
# --------------------------------------------------
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore, revert
# Scope: (optional) e.g., eks, ecr, auth, ui
# BREW-XXX: Jira task link/ID
EOF